{"type":null,"faqId":48060,"title":"升级手机","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.3784722in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.s4{color:blue;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178043\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <span>使用非授权第三方软件升级手机的固件和系统，可能存在手机无法使用或者泄漏您个人信息等安全风险。建议您使用在线升级或者下载与手机型号匹配的官方软件进行升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span>手机升级后，您所有的个人信息可能会被移除，请在升级前备份个人信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">在线升级</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"升级\"XE \"在线升级\"XE \"网络升级\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>在进行在线升级手机之前，请确保手机已连接到网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178044\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">2.  </span><span>在“全部设置”页签下，点击“系统更新”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s3\">3.  </span><span>点击“检查更新”。若有新版本，可按照屏幕提示完成下载和安装。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178045\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>在线升级需要耗费一定的流量，建议在 WLAN 环境下升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">本地升级</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"升级\"XE \"本地升级\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"本地升级\"在进行本地升级之前，请先进入 </span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s4\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/</span></a><span> 下载软件升级包，并将软件升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入手机内部存储的根目录下。如果手机支持 microSD 卡，您还可以将其放入 microSD 卡的根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178046\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>2.在“全部设置”页签下，点击“系统更新”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178047\" style=\"width:0.25694445in;height:0.18333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 本地升级”，按照屏幕提示完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3646","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598106000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":570,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}